=Episode 1=

16
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:06,320
Move. The carriage is coming.

17
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,090
Little trinkets.

18
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,540
You two stay here, okay?

19
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:15,760
- Don't run off.
- Okay.

20
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:17,340
Today's vegetables

21
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,260
